name: Mu Meme
description: Mu MEME is another token in the Mu Ecosytem. It is used for "MEMEing" in our ecosystem. MEMEing in our ecosystem refers to non-standard services provided by the ecosytem. A stardard service would be paying your subscription to our software (not memeing), a non-standard service would be playing the lotto system or minting a Mu NTF (memeing). There are several fun ways to MEME in our ecosystem using Mu Meme.
